{"tid":568892,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"自從開始左冥想後，發覺原來上得多連登係會令大腦疲勞","createTime":"2018-02-22T08:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T11:06:53.000Z","uid":123335,"like":118,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6e63182be346b7d11198ce5a38bfe2ab9b10a1f7","tid":568892,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:14:45.000Z","msg":"開始左冥想後，個腦專注返當下，進入心流，無我既狀態 <br />\n大腦得以休息<br />\n以往積落大腦既疲勞，終於得以解放<br />\n<br />\n先至發覺<br />\n以往上咁多連登<br />\n其實好浪費精神<br />\n係導致大腦疲勞既主因<br />\n<br />\n因為大腦疲勞<br />\n然後就繼續 on99 咁上連登<br />\n造成惡性循環咁脫離不了連登<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老老實實<br />\n上得多連登真係好攰<br />\n垃圾資訊不斷湧入大腦，毫無營養<br />\n但上得多又會被同化左脫離不了，會繼續上<br />\n<br />\n就好像一個不斷循環食屎既過程<br />\n永無止境"},{"pid":"978bf7a4eca21ebd7749f73fccfcfc7f47113085","tid":568892,"uid":123335,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"連登就好似你電腦上d 垃圾程式咁<br />\n會不斷咁食晒你d ram <br />\n搞慢晒你個副engine"},{"pid":"41de4e7a1522aaccdba525f6431154a438549195","tid":568892,"uid":136860,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"咁你仲上黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d95f43bf38432821f7cb8c76ec0890a83831995","tid":568892,"uid":55375,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"好多人鳩碌social media鳩上網都係純粹搵野occupy自己"},{"pid":"3c3743fa47be2fd051261b0fff0cefc7dcc4d0da","tid":568892,"uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"41de4e7a1522aaccdba525f6431154a438549195","tid":568892,"uid":136860,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"咁你仲上黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"你慢慢會越來越少見到我"},{"pid":"6d3e0e8b279c00afc9ba1fa2f1b4db97fe2077ba","tid":568892,"uid":115510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e63182be346b7d11198ce5a38bfe2ab9b10a1f7","tid":568892,"ui